         <ab>VrS50.7 (mss. 2000, 2035):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ka dō-hōmaāst yazēd ka yasn sar guft tā <em>vīspąmcā aməṣ̌ą spəṇtą yazamaide aṣ̌əm vohū</em> sē guftan</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "When he performs a Dō-Hōmāst, when (the priest) has said the end of the Yasn until <em>vīspąmcā aməṣ̌ą spəṇtą yazamaide</em>, they should recite three <em>Aṣ̌əm Vohū</em>."</ab>
